## Tailwind standalone CLI — 108 MB, exceeds GitHub's 100 MB limit.
## Restored automatically on build (see EnsureTailwindCli target in heegarcom.csproj).
tools/tailwindcss.exe

## NOTE: heegarcom/wwwroot/css/app.css (Tailwind output) is intentionally COMMITTED.
## Blazor registers static assets from the wwwroot glob at project-load time, so a
## purely build-generated file never becomes a served endpoint (404 in production).
## Committing it makes it a first-class asset; the build overwrites it with fresh CSS.

